achievements.title: Summer Internship programme

achievements.title: Shaping Integrity and Leadership in medicine
achievements.description: Medicine is not only about science but also about humanity,and this session taught me how to embody both.By practicing professionalsim,I learned that integrity and empathy are true markers of physicians.As soon it start earlier it will benefit in clinical practice.Every session pushed me to grow beyond my comfort zone and embrace responsibility wth confidence.It will my interaction skill with patient.This journey also remind me great doctors built on character as much as knowledge

achievements.title: `Stage to Screen:Master your presenting skills`
achievements.description: Through this I learned how to present ideas with clarity,connect with audience and express thoughts efectively.Now I can present with no fear.

achievements.title: Early Clinical Exposure
achievements.description: In ECE,I interact with patient as first year mbbs and this is very exciting experience but also very nervous.I learned about BLS include CPR and also cvs examination

reflections.title: Dissection of Lower limb
reflections.content: It is very exciting,learning and at first also a little bit fearful experience.I can easily integrate theory with practical.I saw sartorius and quadriceps muscles.It was challanging to remove fascia carefully by not cutting any strcture beneath it.I felt Soleus that is called peripheral heart.I also touch tough tendocalcaneus

reflections.title: Template/Psychology of patient/
reflections.content: When I Observed and interact with patient on ECE,I reazlized that patient`s psychology is also play a vital role in recovery.At times there is no illness but psychological issues manifest as symptoms.this experience taught me healing is noy only limited to treating disease.So doctor must take care both body and psychology of patient by active listening etc.My own experience as a dental patient made me to think that.

reflections.title: Walking For Breath
reflections.content: On World Lung Day,I joined awareness HLF walk that proved to be insightful experience.Although the extreme summer conditions limited full event,the activity offered valuable learning and interaction.It strengthen my understanding of the importance of community awareness

reflections.title: Awareness about silent disease
reflections.content: Participating in fatty liver awareness activities highlighted the importance of lifestyle choices in preventing disease.Otherwise it can lead to cirrhosis.There is no as such apprroved medications,the only way is balanced diet.

reflections.title: Template/Lifestyle Medicine/
reflections.content: Exploring lifestyle medicine opened my eyes to the power of small daily choices in shaping long term health.I learned how nutrition,exercise,sleep, and stress management form true pillars of prevention.This experience deepened my perspective on prevention alongside treatment and strengthen my beleif that every doctor is also guide towards balance lifestyle
